  <section>
    <h2>Container Queries</h2>
    <p>In grid mode, the card uses <code>container-type: inline-size</code> and automatically adjusts padding and typography when placed in narrow containers (under 300px). Headings shrink and footer actions stack vertically.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Accessibility</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>In grid mode, use semantic HTML elements (<code>header</code>, <code>section</code>, <code>footer</code>) for proper document structure</li>
      <li>Include headings in the header area for screen reader navigation</li>
      <li>Footer actions should be keyboard accessible</li>
      <li>Consider wrapping in <code>article</code> if the card represents standalone content</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

